<!-- ═══════════════════ CHAPTER 1 ═══════════════════ -->
<div class="page ch-1">
  <hr class="chapter-rule">
  <div class="chapter-header">
    <div class="ch-pill ch-1-pill">Chapter 1</div>
    <h2>The Day Zara Met ZIPP</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="spread">
    <div class="spread-text">
      <h2>A Robot Arrives! 🎉</h2>
      <p>It was a rainy Tuesday when Zara found a blinking silver box on her doorstep. Inside, there was a small round robot with big blue eyes and a glowing green tummy.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:12px">"Hello!" it chirped. "I am <strong>ZIPP</strong> — a Zing-Intelligent-Processing-Pal. But you can just call me Zipp!"</p>
    </div>
    <div class="scene-box">
      🌧️<br>📦<br>🤖
      <div class="scene-label">A surprise delivery!</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dialogue">
    <div class="chat-avatar">👧</div>
    <div class="bubble zara">"Are you alive? Can you feel things? Do you dream?"</div>
  </div>
  <div class="dialogue right">
    <div class="chat-avatar">🤖</div>
    <div class="bubble robot">"Great questions! I am a machine, but I am very clever. I learn from information — just like you learn from school! I do not dream, but I do <em>think</em>… a LOT."</div>
  </div>

  <div class="fact-box teal">
    <div class="fact-icon">💡</div>
    <p><strong>Fun Fact:</strong> The word "Artificial Intelligence" was invented in 1956 — before your parents, grandparents, or even most great-grandparents were born! Scientists always dreamed of building smart machines.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════ CHAPTER 2 ═══════════════════ -->
<div class="page ch-2">
  <hr class="chapter-rule">
  <div class="chapter-header">
    <div class="ch-pill ch-2-pill">Chapter 2</div>
    <h2>How Does ZIPP Think? 🧠</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="spread">
    <div class="scene-box">
      🧩 + 📚 + 🖼️<br>⬇️<br>✨ Answer!
      <div class="scene-label">How AI learns step by step</div>
    </div>
    <div class="spread-text">
      <h2>Think of a Super Sponge</h2>
      <p>Zipp explained that AI works like a <strong>giant sponge</strong>. It soaks up millions of pictures, words, sounds, and numbers. Then, when you ask it something, it squeezes all that knowledge out to give you the best answer!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dialogue">
    <div class="chat-avatar">👧</div>
    <div class="bubble zara">"But HOW do you learn, Zipp? Do you go to school like me?"</div>
  </div>
  <div class="dialogue right">
    <div class="chat-avatar">🤖</div>
    <div class="bubble robot">"Not exactly! Humans show me thousands of examples. If I see 10,000 pictures of cats, I learn what a cat looks like. If I read 1,000,000 stories, I learn how stories work. More examples = smarter Zipp! 🐱📖"</div>
  </div>

  <div class="fact-box purple">
    <div class="fact-icon">🌟</div>
    <p><strong>Did You Know?</strong> Some AI systems have read more books than every human who has ever lived — combined! Imagine having that many ideas swirling around in your head.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="activity-box">
    <h3>🎨 Try It Yourself!</h3>
    <div class="steps">
